ZH: 明天将会在法院开庭审理这起案件。
EN: The court will open for trial of this case tomorrow.

ZH: 在开庭之前，法官会进行一些准备工作。
EN: Before the court opens, the judge will make some preparations.

ZH: 律师们都在为开庭做准备。
EN: The lawyers are all preparing for the court session.

ZH: 这个案件将于下周在法庭开庭。
EN: This case will open in court next week.

ZH: 昨天我们去了法院，看了一场开庭审判。
EN: Yesterday we went to court and watched a trial session.

ZH: 律师正在庭前等待开庭。
EN: The lawyer is waiting in the courtroom for the trial to begin.

ZH: 开庭前要准备好所有证据。
EN: All evidence must be prepared before the court session.

ZH: 这是一个非常重要的开庭案件。
EN: This is a very important court trial.

ZH: 法官宣布正式开庭。
EN: The judge announced the court session officially open.

ZH: 今天下午将会在法庭开庭。
EN: The court session will open this afternoon.

ZH: 律师表示对开庭结论感到满意。
EN: The lawyer expressed satisfaction with the result of the court trial.

ZH: 开庭过程中出现了一些意外情况。
EN: Some unexpected situations occurred during the court session.

ZH: 法官会主持整个开庭过程。
EN: The judge will preside over the entire court session.

ZH: 开庭时间可能会有变动，请留意通知。
EN: The court session time may change, please pay attention to the notice.

ZH: 开庭日期已确定，敬请准时到场。
EN: The court session date has been confirmed, please arrive on time.

ZH: 案件将在本周五的开庭中审理。
EN: The case will be heard in court this Friday.

ZH: 开庭的宣誓仪式刚刚结束。
EN: The swearing-in ceremony for the court session has just ended.

ZH: 开庭过程中需要所有相关当事人出席。
EN: All relevant parties must be present during the court session.

ZH: 开庭定于周二上午九点开始。
EN: The court session is scheduled to start at 9 am on Tuesday.

ZH: 总统的儿子将在下周的开庭中受审。
EN: The president's son will stand trial in court next week.
